    {
        "content": "<p>Note that <code>instance : ∀ {X Y : Type} [Foo Y], 3 = 3 → Foo X := sorry</code> is a bad instance, because there's no valid synthesization order. Perhaps a similar check could be done before using local parameters in typeclass search</p>",
